\par 12-4-03: RUNT 3.1 released!
\par 
\par RUNT 3.1 has been released. The kernel has been updated to 2.4.23.
\par 
\par A module is now available for the Cypress SL811HS USB host controller. I know nothing about this 
device or what uses it, so I did not include it on the bootdisk for this release. If it would be useful to anyone to be able to boot a usb-storage device connected with such a controller, please email me and I will include this in future releases
